channel.title: How do i gzip a model?
channel.description:
yeah i found out whats wrong with my models i dont know how to gzip them 0o can someone tell me how or send me the program that does.
My friend sent me a gzip application but when i stick it in the folder with the file i wanna gzip the black box opens and closes really fast. I got lucky with a print screen shot and got the full msg it was saying which was:
"gzip: compressed data not written to a terminal. Use -f to force compression. For help, type: gzip -h"
thats what the black box says when it pops up :S
any one help me please :S
